<page>
  <h1>纯净矿石</h1>
  <h3>来源</h3>
  <text>
    <style color="0xaaaaaa" italic="true" pwt="true">注释：本页转载于MCMOD的GTCEu维基<br/>作者：<style color="0xa4e7ff" hover-info="url" pwt="true" underlined="true" url-link="https://center.mcmod.cn/119280/">Oganesson897</style>，<br/> <style color="0xa4e7ff" hover-info="url" underlined="true" url-link="https://github.com/blackdragon2447">BlackDragon2447</style> <br/></style>
  </text>
  <text>
    <style color="0xaaaaaa">（纯净矿石是矿石处理的中间产品，有关任何矿石的具体加工步骤，请参见 JEI/REI/EMI 中的矿物处理流程图。）</style>
  </text>
  <br/>
  <text>纯净矿石是通过<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/ore_washer" underlined="true">洗矿厂</style>或<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/chemical_bath" underlined="true">化学浸洗机</style>（不是每种矿石都行）处理<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:materials/crushed_ore" underlined="true">粉碎矿石</style>获得的，这两种工艺会产生不同的副产品。可以继续用<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/macerator" underlined="true">研磨机</style>或<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/forge_hammer" underlined="true">锻造锤</style>加工成<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:materials/purified_dust" underlined="true">纯净粉</style>，或在<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/thermal_centrifuge" underlined="true">热力离心机</style>中加工成<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:materials/refined_ore" underlined="true">精炼矿石</style>。</text>
